      "name": "Note: Diff the Two Systems"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Create Missing in MySQL\n\nmySql — `insert` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Gather Sync Results · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 MySQL connection",
